    {
      "id": "2f132010-234e-4875-8e3b-411742c599da",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Work uses data from 59 students on the LMS to cluster students according to their interactions with the environment. Authors identify some interesting common patterns related to usage: e.g. students spend more time on lecture related materials. Clustering of the students revealed 3 main groups: “consistent use”, “Slide intensive use” and “less use”. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "2f132010-234e-4875-8e3b-411742c599da",
        "parent": {
